### 1. Session Expiry Policies
- **User-Friendly Notifications**: To enhance user experience, implement a modal that appears when the session is nearing expiration. This modal can provide options such as "Extend Session" and "Log Out." You can use libraries like [React Modal](https://reactcommunity.org/react-modal/) for easy implementation.

